init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are also learning to work together, and to hide who they are from the aliens.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This has made Lia one of the most trusted people in the resistance.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But before they strike, Lia receives a request for help from an unexpected source.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The journey is long and hard, but Lia finally arrives.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They reach the resistance army, and the stage is set for a final confrontation between Mana wielders of all levels once again taking on the alien invaders.
